#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/polynomial/hermite_e.py:docstring
#: of numpy.polynomial.hermite_e.hermevander:33
msgid ""
"The pseudo-Vandermonde matrix. The shape of the returned matrix is ``x.shape "
"+ (deg + 1,)``, where The last index is the degree of the corresponding "
"HermiteE polynomial.  The dtype will be the same as the converted `x`."
msgstr ""

